data.description: Welcome to your fully renovated turnkey 1st floor unit condo in the heart of a vibrant 55+ active resort-style community! The property has a nice open floor plan and been completely updated with brand new a/c, hot water heater, updated kitchen bathroom and flooring, nothing to do but bring the furniture. This is a great opportunity to own a rare 1st floor unit. To help visualize this home's floorplan and to highlight its potential, virtual furnishings may have been added to photos found in this listing
